name: North Cat Token
description: North Cat Token (NCT) takes this fervor to new heights by weaving together a narrative of courage, loyalty, and determination. It's more than just a token; it's a symbol of solidarity among those who choose to live like a cat and defend the honor of the Northern Kingdom. Join us on this journey as we explore the significance of NCT and its mission to safeguard the North.
